data.description: New price! Don't miss your opportunity to own this beautiful, three bedroom home!  This house is on a cul-de-sac street lined with mature trees.  The main floor has plenty of windows which allows natural light to flow in.  The living room showcases a cozy fireplace.  Recent updates include interior paint (2023), roof replacement (2023), water heater replacement (2022) and main floor toilet replacement (2023).  Basement includes a finished room and hook up for an additional, full bathroom.  Enjoy a fenced in back yard and long driveway that leads to a built in garage.  Hurry to see before it's gone!
